data.description: Spacious two story home in sought after Alamo Ranch community. Pristine DR Horton Emerald Series home appointed with large tile, island kitchen, granite counters, spacious primary suite and additional bedroom with full ensuite down. Upstairs features 3 large bedrooms with game room. Covered back patio and ample sized yard create a perfect setting for lounging or entertaining. Exceptional neighborhood amenities with pool, park and sport court. Ideal far west side location near top rated schools, shopping, and dining.
